00:35:34.852 --> 00:35:38.961
at 11 am UTC sharp, here in the same track.

00:35:38.986 --> 00:35:42.143
The host for the next few
talks would be Amanda Bailey.

00:35:42.168 --> 00:35:47.169
I would like to personally give shout out
to the session manager, Stefano;

00:35:47.194 --> 00:35:50.732
our chat monitor, Monique, Hareesh,

00:35:50.756 --> 00:35:55.521
and also to Joe Dolson
for being the lead organizer

00:35:55.546 --> 00:36:00.963
and putting up such an amazing
team with efficiency and success.

00:36:00.988 --> 00:36:03.083
Until the next talk happens,

00:36:03.428 --> 00:36:06.726
we want to say goodbye to the viewers
from Calum and myself.

00:36:06.750 --> 00:36:08.468
See you right here after the break.

00:36:08.493 --> 00:36:09.507
Bye bye.